                                <layout><p>single line of Greek letters, only partly preserved</p>
                                    <rs type="execution" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1">Engraved
                                    </rs>
                                </layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>
                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote><p>Orsi describes it as 'scritta a buone lettere', and his drawing shows slightly irregular broad square and simple letters: alpha with straight bar; rho with closed eye; kappa with long arms of equal length; epsilon with approximately equal bars.</p>
